# State

## Shape

- **One** root aggregate; **only nested slice objects** — no loose fields on root.
- **Immutable** updates (replace slice references).

## Access

| Consumer | Read | Write |
|----------|------|-------|
| Controllers / operations | **Getter** | **Setter** (operations **only**) |
| React | Via **viewmodel** + `useContextSelector` | Never |

## Rules

- Slices are **domain-owned** under `src/domain/<domain>/state/`.
- React **never** imports setters directly.

## Good / bad

```ts
// BAD — component imports setter
import { setCatalog } from '../state';

// GOOD — operation
this.state.setCatalog(nextImmutableSlice);
```
